creator: ISPE
descriptionHtml:
The ISPE App gives you on-the-go access to all things ISPE. Whether you're an ISPE Member or industry professional participating in an ISPE event, this app will meet your needs securely in just a few clicks. Renew your membership, read the latest articles from Pharmaceutical Engineering® magazine and iSpeak, the official blog of ISPE, check out upcoming ISPE events, connect with colleagues, and so much more!

Key Features Include:
• Pay your membership dues or become a Member
• Access your ISPE Communities of Practice*
• View the membership directory*
• Use Member-to-Member messaging*
• Access event content for our in-person and virtual events including networking, building a custom agenda, exhibit hall, and more
• Read Pharmaceutical Engineering® magazine articles
• Discover the latest industry articles
• Explore online resources
• And so much more!

Download the ISPE app now to make the most out of your membership and/or event experience!

*You must be an ISPE Member to use these features.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Quick Search Bar in Directory
- New Stock Photos for Events
- Ability to see a list of sessions' live streaming URLs
- Podcasts
- Additional News module
- Ability to access handouts from the Event Dashboard
- New widgets on Home: Resource Library and Alerts
- Ability for the attendees to opt-out of the event attendee list
- Alternative app login method using email OTP
- New empty state and alert screens throughout the app
- Design improvements
- Performance improvements
- Bug Fixes
